<%= program_title('Participants', 'users') %>  

<p class="alert alert-info">
There are currently <strong><%= User.count %> users</strong> registered at the Siam-is18 website.<br/>
The Partecipant List only shows the names of those users that have given explicit permission to publish their name.<br/>
If your name does not appear in the Partecipant List, please log in (sign in, using your credentials) and tick the flag 'Show in SIAM-IS18 page' in your personal data.
</p>

<%# link_to 'see where participants come from', countries_stats_path, class: :button %>  

<% initial = nil %>
<dl class='dl-horizontal'>
  <% @participants.each do |user| %> 
    <% if initial != (initial = user.surname[0].upcase) %>  
      <dd>&nbsp;</dd>
      <dt><%= initial %></dt>
    <% end %>
  <dd><%= @link_to_user ? user_modal_link(user) : user.cn %> <small>(<%= user.affiliation %>)</small></dd>
<% end %>
</dl>
